'''Ayoka Olufunmilayo Adebambo''' yin lẹnnuyọnẹtọ [[Naijilia|Naijilia]] podọ mẹplọntọ gando kanlin yìnyìn  podo kunkan yetọn lẹ po. E yin wesetọ  yọnnu tintan he plọn gando kanlinlin yìnyìn podo kunkan kanlin tọn po. To Zósun 2010, e yin nina ajọ̀  na e yin dopo to hagbẹ Animal Science Association of Nigeria (ASAN).

